{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ensure access to school for children with ASDs/mental health issues during Covid",
        "additional_details": "Many children with hidden ASD\u2019s and/or Mental Health issues suffered immensely during lockdown which had an adverse effect on their families has whole.\r\n \r\nHaving to work from home and hold down a job (without the respite that schooling offers to parents) whilst tending to the additional emotional, physical and educational needs of a child with diagnosed mental health/ASD is unjust.\r\n",
        "background": "When schools were closed in March they remained open to the children of critical workers and some vulnerable children. I want the Government to ensure that if schools are closed again that all children with Autism Spectrum Disorders/Mental Health issues are able to continue to attend school.",
